## Screen order

Splash → Onboarding (1/3, 2/3, 3/3) → Log In → Sign up → Home → History → Services → Nearby Courier → Track Order → Calculate/Ship Parcel → Menu/Profile/FAQ/Help → Chat/Notification

Default reference: **Light Version** frames (y≈2469 row in Figma).

